    "This includes the internal control species I. halotolerans and A. halotolerans (Figures 3C, D).",
    "As SNPs in genes encoding target enzymes are an important mechanism of FQ resistance (Kherroubi et al., 2024), the MAGs in both samples were screened, but initially no FQ resistance SNPs were found.",
    "However, as MAGs often represent a specieslevel consensus, they can mask low-frequency FQ resistant strains.",
    "Therefore, we performed a haplotype-phasing analysis (Figure 1D), focused on FQ resistance for several MAGs that were indicated as having high strain heterogeneity (Table 2).",
    "In sample A, two phased assemblies were produced for the E. coli MAG: a first (phased 1) detected at a coverage of 31.3X, with high completeness and reduced contamination than the original MAG; and a second (phased 2) at a lower coverage of 11.9X, with lower completeness and higher contamination than the original MAG (Table 2, Supplementary Figure S3)."
  ],
